About

A public servant and software developer, I'm a career-changer on the lookout for the next opportunity in Wellington.

Tech aligns with my skills and interest in project coordination, collaborative problem-solving, and continual learning. In pursuit of a challenge, I started teaching myself how to code last year and haven’t looked back.

Completing the bootcamp at Dev Academy Aotearoa further ignited a love for working with others to create well-designed applications. Creating technical solutions to help others and writing clean code excite me, and I’m looking forward to learning more.

Check out my projects and resume!

) }
